name: Terry and the Twelve Chips of Power
name_original: Terry and the Twelve Chips of Power
description:
You are Terry the seagull. You and your wife Tina have been on a very long journey across the Atlantic. You need to replenish your power by gathering the 12 chips of power.

Controls:

Space to jump.

This is my first game project that is completable. Looking forward to doing more.
